    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE ISSUANCE OF STATE GENERAL OBLIGATION BONDS TO PROVIDE FUNDS TO ASSIST THE CITY OF GREENWOOD, MISSISSIPPI, IN PAYING COSTS ASSOCIATED WITH THE ACQUISITION OF ESSENTIAL MUNICIPAL VEHICLES FOR CERTAIN CITY DEPARTMENTS AND RETIRING OR REDUCING EXISTING LONG-TERM DEBT OBLIGATIONS INCURRED TO ACQUIRE AND MAINTAIN MUNICIPAL VEHICLES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
